@startuml

[*] --> AddNewGoods

state "Add New Goods" as AddNewGoods
state "Update Price" as UpdatePrice
state "Remove Goods" as RemoveGoods
state "Identify Expired Goods" as IdentifyExpiredGoods
state "Place Order" as PlaceOrder
state "Generate Invoice" as GenerateInvoice
state "Search Items" as SearchItems
state "Calculate Discount and Tax" as CalculateDiscountTax
state "Generate Receipt" as GenerateReceipt
state "Replace Item or Cancel Receipt" as ReplaceItemCancelReceipt
state "Record Customer Requests" as RecordCustomerRequests
state "View Summary Report" as ViewSummaryReport

AddNewGoods --> UpdatePrice : add new goods
UpdatePrice --> RemoveGoods : update price
RemoveGoods --> IdentifyExpiredGoods : remove goods
IdentifyExpiredGoods --> PlaceOrder : identify expired goods
PlaceOrder --> GenerateInvoice : place order
GenerateInvoice --> SearchItems : generate invoice
SearchItems --> CalculateDiscountTax : search items
CalculateDiscountTax --> GenerateReceipt : calculate discount and tax
GenerateReceipt --> ReplaceItemCancelReceipt : generate receipt
ReplaceItemCancelReceipt --> RecordCustomerRequests : replace item or cancel receipt
RecordCustomerRequests --> ViewSummaryReport : record customer requests

ViewSummaryReport --> [*] : COMPLETION_EVENT

@enduml
